                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990911-98-defend785 t17990911-98-punish536"></join>
               Whipped in the jail
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
